The paper deals with control design for continuous-time systems, which falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY). The proposed method is based on optimization, specifically sum-of-absolute-values (SOAV) optimization, which suggests that the paper could also belong to the optimization (cs.Optimization) category. The paper also mentions the use of an algorithm, which could indicate that it belongs to the machine learning (cs.LG) or numerical analysis (cs.NA) categories. Finally, the paper deals with stability analysis, which could suggest that it belongs to the control engineering (cs.CE) category.
